{"tid":371294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB半年盈利大跌44%　政府廣告收入卻倍增","createTime":"2017-08-23T15:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T16:13:49.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8922515f7f1e5814c0fd43bd1f08b91fdda8f7b9","tid":371294,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"「大台」電視廣播（0511　TVB）公佈今年上半年中期業績，純利按年下跌44%至1.7億元。TVB在業績提到，因香港特別行政區成立20周年的多項慶祝活動，取得多個政府及相關廣告訂單，「政府╱半官方機構」類別的廣告收入於2017年上半年錄得接近100%增幅。<br />\n<br />\n公司宣布派中期股息每股0.3元，少於去年同期之0.6元。<br />\n<br />\n翻查紀錄，TVB在今年上半年賺1.7億元，至少是近六年最差的中期業績。相比2015年上半年，TVB盈利高達11.5億元，今年上半年盈利跌了八成半。<br />\n<br />\n期內，香港電視廣播業務的廣告收入穩定，收入按年升3%至20.21億元，持續經營業務的成本總額（包括開發新平台myTV SUPER及大台網所增加的成本）由16.78億元上升至18.1億元，升幅為8%；經營溢利錄得2.96億元，按年跌幅為9%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，TVB期內因預留42億元回購股份的資金，損失賺取利息收益的機會，加上去年同售出售TVBS合營公司股權錄得7100萬元的特殊收益，致純利按年跌44%至1.7億元。"},{"pid":"546da1e737d5f30cec1b514293b5703659f0aeef","tid":371294,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:09:07.000Z","msg":"政府送錢比cctvv,倍增好正常"},{"pid":"4c7a17919ecbb26ecd8214b2005e8a53bdcf7dd9","tid":371294,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府送錢比cctvv,倍增好正常</blockquote><br />\n納稅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91994eac2db7ab970bd47302370a5faced93383b","tid":371294,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府送錢比cctvb,倍增好正常</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b4187585ffa7df7268b054101d787441dc82b634","tid":371294,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>政府送錢比cctvb,倍增好正常</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n政府做埋大股東喇"},{"pid":"685d286543ae94436406cd1b9219a2078cf8ed11","tid":371294,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"共產黨對香港TVB的文化攻擊[電影,音樂,APPS,遊戲(eg.LOL)等]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/337932/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/337932/page/2?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e9827368a351510d7e769cd1d6727c4350e43a1","tid":371294,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"用納稅人錢日日播膠鐵廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ceeaafa347122ac2b92283960ab09a600be777","tid":371294,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾時回購tvb"},{"pid":"db917e3aaed6680aa1a08428aac31a6a9e276c79","tid":371294,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:13:49.000Z","msg":"洗腦廣告"}]}